(*Eccentricity corrections to the SEOBNRv5 modes*)


(* ::Text:: *)
(*The EOB modes are factorized as*)
(*h[l, m] = h_lm^(N, qc) Seff T_lm f_lm^qc E^(i \[Delta]_lm^qc) hFactEccCorr[l, m]*)
